Father Joseph Witko: I saw Jesus in a white robe
He's charismatic.
For the Holy Masses he celebrates, the crowds gather for liberation and healing.
He was ten years old when inexplicable things began to happen in his life.
Today, through the Franciscan, others experience this.
At the Holy Masses celebrated by Fr Witko for the release and healing of the crowds
He was once visited by the parents of a 7-month-old child who had a 7.5 mm hole in his heart.
It was supposed to be operated on.
Father Joseph Witko prayed over him.
The same day, the boy was taken to the hospital for treatment.
Astonished, the doctors said: “There is no need for surgery, the defect is only 1.5 mm.”
My parents were crying with happiness.
After another prayer, the Franciscan hole disappeared completely.
The priest began to experience the unusual actions of the Creator as a teenager.
In his dreams, purgatory souls came to him to ask for help.
I was awakened at night and urged to pray for the dead and those who were dying in the moment.
He also experienced the presence of an evil spirit.
And he had a vision of what happens to a man who commits mortal sin.
“My body began to change.
I lost my human characteristics and began to take on the appearance of an animal," he says.
An invisible force lifted him up, he could not get his voice out.
He felt he was lost.
Then God showed him salvation.
“Immersed in the waters of the river symbolizing holy baptism, I was released and returned to my human form,” he says.
He didn't tell anyone about these strange experiences.
There was a calling in him.
He was 16 years old when he joined the Franciscans.
In his sermons, he did not just want to talk about Jesus.
He wanted people to experience him alive.
Members of the Charismatic Community of Renewal in the Holy Spirit
Many people who count on getting rid of the disease participate in the healing Masses celebrated by Father Witko.
However, the priest emphasizes that their main goal is spiritual healing, not physical.
